As a user
I want to find a poll
So that I may express my opinion

Scenario: User searches for a poll with valid HTML request
    When I submit my request
    Then The server searches for matching polls
    And I am brought to the results page

Scenario: User searches for a poll with valid XML request
    When I submit my request
    Then The server searches for matching polls
    And I am brought to the results page
    
Scenario: User searches for a poll with valid JSON request
    When I submit my request
    Then The server searches for matching polls
    And I am brought to the results page